00:36:29.600 --> 00:36:32.960
and what do we even mean
by whether or not it should

00:36:32.960 --> 00:36:35.730
be valued in a way or not.

00:36:35.730 --> 00:36:38.870
And finally, we're going to
ask the question for valuation,

00:36:38.870 --> 00:36:41.660
how well do financial
