00:59:22.500 --> 00:59:23.820
That's the same for finance.

00:59:23.820 --> 00:59:25.740
Finance is not a
spectator sport.

00:59:25.740 --> 00:59:27.360
You actually have to do it.

00:59:27.360 --> 00:59:31.080
You have to confront yourself
with problems time and again,

00:59:31.080 --> 00:59:33.870
and think about how to apply
the principles in our lecture

00:59:33.870 --> 00:59:36.120
to those problems.

