01:00:01.840 --> 01:00:04.830
So it's going to cover twice
the material as the midterm.

01:00:04.830 --> 01:00:08.160
Therefore it should be
worth roughly double.

01:00:08.160 --> 01:00:12.820
But the other reason is
that financial analysis

01:00:12.820 --> 01:00:17.630
is alien to the typical
human cognitive process.

01:00:17.630 --> 01:00:21.040
None of you are hard wired to
